SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], [s].[ID] AS [IdSegmento], [s].[NOMBRE] AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
